title: FEC Releases Final Audit Report on the Democratic State Central Committee of Maryland
html:
News Releases, Media Advisories

April 7, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
THE DEMOCRATIC STATE CENTRAL COMMITTEE OF MARYLAND
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on the Democratic State Central Committee of Maryland. This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
